#: plugin/admin/partner-discount/partner-discount-ui.php:114
msgid ""
"This privacy-compliant WordPress analytics plugin gives detailed insights "
"into user behavior beyond what traditional tools can provide, and has a "
"dedicated integration for WooCommerce."
msgstr ""
"Ce plugin d’analyse WordPress respectueux de la confidentialité donne des "
"informations détaillées sur le comportement des utilisateurs au-delà de ce "
